  <name>MOV MetaEdit</name>
  <summary>Embed and edit Universal Ad ID metadata in MOV or MP4 files</summary>
  <description>
    <p>MOV MetaEdit is a tool that supports the embedding and editing of metadata in MOV (Apple QuickTime)
      or MP4 (ISO/IEC 14496-14 a.k.a. MPEG-4 Part 14) files.</p>
    <p>It is currently focused on Universal Ad ID metadata but could be expanded on request.</p>
    <p>Sponsored by Ad-ID; designed, led and fully developed by MediaArea.</p>
  </description>
